#### Installation
1. Install dependencies
    
    ```
    npm install
    ```

2. Create a `.env` file by copying the sample

    ```
    cp .env_sample .env
    ```
    
    Now edit the .env file and replace the `IMGUR_CLIENT_ID` with the client ID provided in the pre-installation
    
3. Start project

    ```
    npm run start
    ```

4. Your site will be available at *localhost:[PORT]* where `PORT` is whatever value is set in your `.env` file.